title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: When attempting to export data from the attached report, an exception is thrown. This occurs specifically when trying to export data from a table that contains a highlight or map.
OB: The user encounters an exception when attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight or map.
EB: The data in the table should be successfully exported without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the attached report. 
2. Export the data from a table that contains a highlight or map. 
3. Observe the exception being thrown when attempting to export the data.
